chasing rubi : the truth about porfirio rubirosa the last playboy i have always had a fascination about porfirio rubirosa and this book makes me realize that he really was the latin james bond and an inspiration for the subsequent books and movies . the book contains truely interesting no where else to be found facts and is written in such an easy to read way . i think that anybody that has ever enjoyed a james bond movie or book should read this book . i am sure that one day this book will be turned into a move